posts.post_title: F/S - HOF and So. Leaguer - PSA Graded
posts.post_content:
F/S are the following (2) individual PSA graded T-206 cards. Payment by Paypal F/F to [url]billscheffel@yahoo.com[/url]. Prices include shipping. Thanks for looking and good luck with your collection. See scans for further details.

1. T206 - Molly Miller (So. League card) - PSA 3, Piedmont 350 back, Factory 25, $120.00

2. T206 - Joe Kelley (HOF- double name on top and bottom) - PSA 5 (MC), Piedmont 350 back, Factory 25, $305.00. 
I believe the MC qualifier is due to the extra large top border, with a partial name on the top edge. See scans for further details.

Thanks for consideration.

Bill
Open to offers on these two cards.
